<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">صُلْحُ الْفُضُولِيِّ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٢ - اتَّفَقَ الْفُقَهَاءُ عَلَى جَرَيَانِ الصُّلْحِ مِنَ الْفُضُولِيِّ كَجَرَيَانِهِ مِمَّنْ عَلَيْهِ الْحَقُّ، وَاخْتَلَفُوا فِي ضِمْنِ ذَلِكَ إِلَى أَقْوَالٍ وَصُوَرٍ وَشُرُوطٍ كَثِيرَةٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَالتَّفْصِيل فِي مُصْطَلَحِ <span class="c2">(صُلْح ف ١٩ - ٢٢)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الْجُزْء الثَّانِي وَالثَّلاَثُونَ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَضِيخ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> أَشْرِبَة<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>